rows.label: qst201913_0010
rows.name:
You can't escape now, you
black-feathered fool.

rows.label: qst201913_0020
rows.name: Give up and return our money.

rows.label: qst201913_0030
rows.name:
I have no money to return to you, mo.
It's your fault for being deceived, mo!

rows.label: qst201913_0040
rows.name: You fiend!

rows.label: qst201913_0050
rows.name: Wait a moment, Rinne!

rows.label: qst201913_0060
rows.name: Divine punishmeeeent!

rows.label: qst201913_0070
rows.name: Mo-mo-mooooooo!

rows.label: qst201913_0080
rows.name: Ahhh... In my anger, I just...

rows.label: qst201913_0090
rows.name: Ah, our money... Our one million gold...

rows.label: qst201913_0100
rows.name: ...is being taken by the rabble...

rows.label: qst201913_0110
rows.name: You've done it now.

rows.label: qst201913_0120
rows.name: I tried to stop you...

rows.label: qst201913_0130
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Ah... ahhh...

rows.label: qst201913_0140
rows.name: Miss...

rows.label: qst201913_0150
rows.name: ...Hmm?

rows.label: qst201913_0160
rows.name: Here. This is yours, isn't it?

rows.label: qst201913_0170
rows.name: You would... return this to us?

rows.label: qst201913_0180
rows.name: Yes. It's hard to get by without money.

rows.label: qst201913_0190
rows.name: Oh, you kind child, you pure angel!

rows.label: qst201913_0200
rows.name: All of you, for our sake...

rows.label: qst201913_0210
rows.name: Thank you, thank you.

rows.label: qst201913_0220
rows.name: ...We were foolish.

rows.label: qst201913_0230
rows.name:
To have doubted you all, even for a moment...
We are ashamed of our own poor heart...

rows.label: qst201913_0240
rows.name: ...Yes, we wish to thank you.

rows.label: qst201913_0250
rows.name: Let us invite you all to a tea party.

rows.label: qst201913_0260
rows.name: Is that okay?

rows.label: qst201913_0270
rows.name: Amazing!

rows.label: qst201913_0280
rows.name:
Huh? Are you planning to
invite everyone here?

rows.label: qst201913_0290
rows.name: Yes. We no longer need this money.

rows.label: qst201913_0300
rows.name:
We have found something
more precious than money.

rows.label: qst201913_0310
rows.name:
We were saved, body and
soul, by these pure angels.

rows.label: qst201913_0320
rows.name:
Our idea of using the power of money to gather
lovers and hold a tea party was wrong.

rows.label: qst201913_0330
rows.name:
What we truly wanted by our side
were girls with such pure hearts.

rows.label: qst201913_0340
rows.name:
By holding a tea party with these
children, our dream will come true.

rows.label: qst201913_0350
rows.name: Rinne... are you sure about this?

rows.label: qst201913_0360
rows.name:
It is still our dream,
for better or worse.

rows.label: qst201913_0370
rows.name:
We have simply realized a
new way to achieve it.

rows.label: qst201913_0380
rows.name: In that case... may I join as well?

rows.label: qst201913_0390
rows.name:
I will join too. May I
have an invitation?

rows.label: qst201913_0400
rows.name: Yes, of course.

rows.label: qst201913_0410
rows.name: This is delicious, miss.

rows.label: qst201913_0420
rows.name: I've never eaten such sweets before.

rows.label: qst201913_0430
rows.name:
Is that so? We are very
happy that you enjoy it.

rows.label: qst201913_0440
rows.name:
Now, everyone else, we have
prepared plenty of sweets and tea.

rows.label: qst201913_0450
rows.name:
Let us enjoy the tea
party to the fullest!

rows.label: qst201913_0460
rows.name: ...Why are we the ones serving?

rows.label: qst201913_0470
rows.name: Tora is not convinced, mo.

rows.label: qst201913_0480
rows.name:
Don't say it. We just have to endure
for now... Being a man is tough.

rows.label: qst201913_0490
rows.name: *sigh*...
